{
  "video_id": "7gkdzkVbuVA",
  "title": "Laura Carstensen: Older people are happier",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 15902.0,
      "end_time": 19801.0,
      "text": "People are living longer and societies are getting grayer."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 20373.0,
      "end_time": 22101.0,
      "text": "You hear about it all the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 22245.0,
      "end_time": 24240.0,
      "text": "You read about it in your newspapers."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 24480.0,
      "end_time": 26394.0,
      "text": "You hear about it on your television sets."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 26418.0,
      "end_time": 27682.0,
      "text": "Sometimes, I&#39;m concerned"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 27706.0,
      "end_time": 32314.0,
      "text": "that we hear about it so much that we&#39;ve come to accept longer lives"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 32338.0,
      "end_time": 36171.0,
      "text": "with a kind of a complacency, even ease."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 37203.0,
      "end_time": 41485.0,
      "text": "But make no mistake, longer lives can --"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 41509.0,
      "end_time": 47392.0,
      "text": "and, I believe, will improve quality of life at all ages."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 48956.0,
      "end_time": 52920.0,
      "text": "Now to put this in perspective, let me just zoom out for a minute."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 53840.0,
      "end_time": 58980.0,
      "text": "More years were added to average life expectancy in the 20th century"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 60154.0,
      "end_time": 67610.0,
      "text": "than all years added across all prior millennia"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 67850.0,
      "end_time": 69259.0,
      "text": "of human evolution combined."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 70535.0,
      "end_time": 72630.0,
      "text": "In the blink of an eye,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 72870.0,
      "end_time": 75459.0,
      "text": "we nearly doubled the length of time that we&#39;re living."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 76685.0,
      "end_time": 79988.0,
      "text": "So if you ever feel like you don&#39;t have this aging thing quite pegged,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 80120.0,
      "end_time": 81326.0,
      "text": "don&#39;t kick yourself."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 81350.0,
      "end_time": 83235.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s brand new."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 83887.0,
      "end_time": 88380.0,
      "text": "And because fertility rates fell across that very same period"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 88620.0,
      "end_time": 90558.0,
      "text": "that life expectancy was going up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 91857.0,
      "end_time": 97448.0,
      "text": "that pyramid that has always represented the distribution of age in the population,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 97472.0,
      "end_time": 102497.0,
      "text": "with many young ones at the bottom winnowed to a tiny peak of older people"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 102522.0,
      "end_time": 104759.0,
      "text": "who make it and survive to old age,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 104783.0,
      "end_time": 108653.0,
      "text": "is being reshaped into a rectangle."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 110728.0,
      "end_time": 112536.0,
      "text": "And now, if you&#39;re the kind of person"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 112560.0,
      "end_time": 114917.0,
      "text": "who can get chills from population statistics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 114941.0,
      "end_time": 115964.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 115988.0,
      "end_time": 117782.0,
      "text": "these are the ones that should do it."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 117806.0,
      "end_time": 119236.0,
      "text": "Because what that means"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 119260.0,
      "end_time": 123100.0,
      "text": "is that for the first time in the history of the species,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 123124.0,
      "end_time": 126893.0,
      "text": "the majority of babies born in the developed world"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 126918.0,
      "end_time": 130734.0,
      "text": "are having the opportunity to grow old."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 132671.0,
      "end_time": 134236.0,
      "text": "How did this happen?"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 134698.0,
      "end_time": 138706.0,
      "text": "Well, we&#39;re no genetically hardier than our ancestors were 10,000 years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 139238.0,
      "end_time": 143550.0,
      "text": "This increase in life expectancy is the remarkable product of culture --"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 144820.0,
      "end_time": 147775.0,
      "text": "the crucible that holds science and technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 147799.0,
      "end_time": 153235.0,
      "text": "and wide-scale changes in behavior that improve health and well-being."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 154419.0,
      "end_time": 160703.0,
      "text": "Through cultural changes, our ancestors largely eliminated early death"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 160727.0,
      "end_time": 163552.0,
      "text": "so that people can now live out their full lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 164784.0,
      "end_time": 167728.0,
      "text": "Now there are problems associated with aging --"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 167753.0,
      "end_time": 170430.0,
      "text": "diseases, poverty, loss of social status."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 170680.0,
      "end_time": 172236.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s hardly time to rest on our laurels."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 173310.0,
      "end_time": 175107.0,
      "text": "But the more we learn about aging,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 175131.0,
      "end_time": 179170.0,
      "text": "the clearer it becomes that a sweeping downward course"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 179194.0,
      "end_time": 181236.0,
      "text": "is grossly inaccurate."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 182214.0,
      "end_time": 185482.0,
      "text": "Aging brings some rather remarkable improvements --"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 185506.0,
      "end_time": 188236.0,
      "text": "increased knowledge, expertise --"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 189365.0,
      "end_time": 193735.0,
      "text": "and emotional aspects of life improve."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 195640.0,
      "end_time": 198999.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s right, older people are happy."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 199788.0,
      "end_time": 203386.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re happier than middle-aged people, and younger people, certainly."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 203410.0,
      "end_time": 204591.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 204616.0,
      "end_time": 207730.0,
      "text": "Study after study is coming to the same conclusion."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 207754.0,
      "end_time": 210585.0,
      "text": "The CDC recently conducted a survey"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 210610.0,
      "end_time": 213494.0,
      "text": "where they asked respondents simply to tell them"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 213518.0,
      "end_time": 216633.0,
      "text": "whether they experienced significant psychological distress"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 216657.0,
      "end_time": 217819.0,
      "text": "in the previous week."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 217843.0,
      "end_time": 221476.0,
      "text": "And fewer older people answered affirmatively to that question"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 221501.0,
      "end_time": 224235.0,
      "text": "than middle-aged people, and younger people as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 225126.0,
      "end_time": 228910.0,
      "text": "And a recent Gallup poll asked participants"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 228115.0,
      "end_time": 232601.0,
      "text": "how much stress and worry and anger they had experienced the previous day."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 232918.0,
      "end_time": 237470.0,
      "text": "And stress, worry, anger"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 237491.0,
      "end_time": 239260.0,
      "text": "all decrease with age."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 240867.0,
      "end_time": 243873.0,
      "text": "Now social scientists call this the paradox of aging."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 243897.0,
      "end_time": 246589.0,
      "text": "I mean, after all, aging is not a piece of cake."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 247351.0,
      "end_time": 251625.0,
      "text": "So we&#39;ve asked all sorts of questions to see if we could undo this finding."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 252659.0,
      "end_time": 258840.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve asked whether it may be that the current generations of older people"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 258601.0,
      "end_time": 261130.0,
      "text": "are and always have been the greatest generations."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 261869.00000000003,
      "end_time": 265537.0,
      "text": "That is that younger people today may not typically experience"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 265561.0,
      "end_time": 267888.0,
      "text": "these improvements as they grow older."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 268487.0,
      "end_time": 269811.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve asked,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 269835.0,
      "end_time": 273777.0,
      "text": "well, maybe older people are just trying to put a positive spin"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 273802.0,
      "end_time": 276215.0,
      "text": "on an otherwise depressing existence."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 276239.0,
      "end_time": 277986.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 278100.0,
      "end_time": 280863.0,
      "text": "But the more we&#39;ve tried to disavow this finding,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 280887.0,
      "end_time": 283385.0,
      "text": "the more evidence we find to support it."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 284806.0,
      "end_time": 287140.0,
      "text": "Years ago, my colleagues and I embarked on a study"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 287165.0,
      "end_time": 290253.0,
      "text": "where we followed the same group of people over a 10-year period."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 290277.0,
      "end_time": 293236.0,
      "text": "Originally, the sample was aged 18 to 94."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 293754.0,
      "end_time": 297930.0,
      "text": "And we studied whether and how their emotional experiences changed"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 297117.0,
      "end_time": 299220.0,
      "text": "as they grew older."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 299460.0,
      "end_time": 302357.0,
      "text": "Our participants would carry electronic pagers"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 302381.0,
      "end_time": 303881.0,
      "text": "for a week at a time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 303906.0,
      "end_time": 307205.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;d page them throughout the day and evenings at random times."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 307229.0,
      "end_time": 309190.0,
      "text": "And every time we paged them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 309430.0,
      "end_time": 311950.0,
      "text": "we&#39;d ask them to answer several questions --"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 311119.0,
      "end_time": 314184.0,
      "text": "\"On a one to seven scale, how happy are you right now?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 314208.0,
      "end_time": 315693.0,
      "text": "\"How sad are you right now?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 315717.0,
      "end_time": 317868.0,
      "text": "\"How frustrated are you right now?\" --"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 317892.0,
      "end_time": 322126.0,
      "text": "so that we could get a sense of the kinds of emotions and feelings they were having"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 322150.0,
      "end_time": 323530.0,
      "text": "in their day-to-day lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 324309.0,
      "end_time": 327603.0,
      "text": "And using this intense study of individuals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 327627.0,
      "end_time": 331481.0,
      "text": "we find that it&#39;s not one particular generation"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 331505.0,
      "end_time": 333766.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s doing better than the others,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 333790.0,
      "end_time": 336664.0,
      "text": "but the same individuals over time"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 336688.0,
      "end_time": 341546.0,
      "text": "come to report relatively greater positive experience."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 341571.0,
      "end_time": 346900.0,
      "text": "Now you see this slight downturn at very advanced ages."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 346330.0,
      "end_time": 347670.0,
      "text": "And there is a slight downturn."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 347694.0,
      "end_time": 352683.0,
      "text": "But at no point does it return to the levels we see in early adulthood."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 353888.0,
      "end_time": 360888.0,
      "text": "Now it&#39;s really too simplistic to say that older people are \"happy.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 361929.0,
      "end_time": 364234.0,
      "text": "In our study, they are more positive."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 365880.0,
      "end_time": 367405.0,
      "text": "But they&#39;re also more likely than younger people"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 367429.0,
      "end_time": 369602.0,
      "text": "to experience mixed emotions --"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 369626.0,
      "end_time": 372243.0,
      "text": "sadness at the same time you experience happiness;"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 372267.0,
      "end_time": 375711.0,
      "text": "you know, that tear in the eye when you&#39;re smiling at a friend."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 376894.0,
      "end_time": 381537.0,
      "text": "And other research has shown that older people seem to engage with sadness"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 381561.0,
      "end_time": 382967.0,
      "text": "more comfortably."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 382991.0,
      "end_time": 385875.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re more accepting of sadness than younger people are."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 385899.0,
      "end_time": 388492.0,
      "text": "And we suspect that this may help to explain"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 388516.0,
      "end_time": 391236.0,
      "text": "why older people are better than younger people"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 391260.0,
      "end_time": 395512.0,
      "text": "at solving hotly charged emotional conflicts and debates."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 397260.0,
      "end_time": 401546.0,
      "text": "Older people can view injustice with compassion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 402220.0,
      "end_time": 403562.0,
      "text": "but not despair."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 404619.0,
      "end_time": 406356.0,
      "text": "And all things being equal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 406380.0,
      "end_time": 410471.0,
      "text": "older people direct their cognitive resources, like attention and memory,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 410495.0,
      "end_time": 413236.0,
      "text": "to positive information more than negative."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 413876.0,
      "end_time": 417227.0,
      "text": "If we show older, middle-aged, younger people images,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 417252.0,
      "end_time": 419236.0,
      "text": "like the ones you see on the screen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 419958.0,
      "end_time": 424584.0,
      "text": "and we later ask them to recall all the images that they can,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 425145.0,
      "end_time": 427503.0,
      "text": "older people, but not younger people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 427528.0,
      "end_time": 431235.0,
      "text": "remember more positive images than negative images."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 431912.0,
      "end_time": 436490.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve asked older and younger people to view faces in laboratory studies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 436740.0,
      "end_time": 437950.0,
      "text": "some frowning, some smiling."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 437974.0,
      "end_time": 443960.0,
      "text": "Older people look toward the smiling faces and away from the frowning, angry faces."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 444517.0,
      "end_time": 449625.0,
      "text": "In day-to-day life, this translates into greater enjoyment and satisfaction."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 451793.0,
      "end_time": 456820.0,
      "text": "But as social scientists, we continue to ask about possible alternatives."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 456106.0,
      "end_time": 459760.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve said, well, maybe older people report more positive emotions"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 459784.0,
      "end_time": 462236.0,
      "text": "because they&#39;re cognitively impaired."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 462260.0,
      "end_time": 465580.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 466136.0,
      "end_time": 467367.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve said, could it be"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 467391.0,
      "end_time": 470985.0,
      "text": "that positive emotions are simply easier to process than negative emotions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 471900.0,
      "end_time": 474178.0,
      "text": "and so you switch to the positive emotions?"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 474202.0,
      "end_time": 476337.0,
      "text": "Maybe our neural centers in our brain"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 476361.0,
      "end_time": 480483.0,
      "text": "are degraded such that we&#39;re unable to process negative emotions anymore."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 480832.0,
      "end_time": 482341.0,
      "text": "But that&#39;s not the case."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 482874.0,
      "end_time": 486110.0,
      "text": "The most mentally sharp older adults"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 486134.0,
      "end_time": 489236.0,
      "text": "are the ones who show this positivity effect the most."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 490209.0,
      "end_time": 492491.0,
      "text": "And under conditions where it really matters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 492515.0,
      "end_time": 495430.0,
      "text": "older people do process the negative information"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 495670.0,
      "end_time": 497236.0,
      "text": "just as well as the positive information."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 497618.0,
      "end_time": 499581.0,
      "text": "So how can this be?"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 501136.0,
      "end_time": 503109.0,
      "text": "Well, in our research,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 503217.0,
      "end_time": 507207.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ve found that these changes are grounded fundamentally"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 507232.0,
      "end_time": 510449.0,
      "text": "in the uniquely human ability to monitor time --"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 510473.0,
      "end_time": 513522.0,
      "text": "not just clock time and calendar time, but lifetime."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 514467.0,
      "end_time": 516486.0,
      "text": "And if there&#39;s a paradox of aging,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 516929.0,
      "end_time": 519931.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s that recognizing that we won&#39;t live forever"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 519956.0,
      "end_time": 524212.0,
      "text": "changes our perspective on life in positive ways."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 525464.0,
      "end_time": 530270.0,
      "text": "When time horizons are long and nebulous, as they typically are in youth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 530294.0,
      "end_time": 532236.0,
      "text": "people are constantly preparing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 532260.0,
      "end_time": 536150.0,
      "text": "trying to soak up all the information they possibly can,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 536390.0,
      "end_time": 538285.0,
      "text": "taking risks, exploring."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 538309.0,
      "end_time": 541252.0,
      "text": "We might spend time with people we don&#39;t even like"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 541276.0,
      "end_time": 543375.0,
      "text": "because it&#39;s somehow interesting."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 543399.0,
      "end_time": 545595.0,
      "text": "We might learn something unexpected."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 545619.0,
      "end_time": 547679.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 547703.0,
      "end_time": 549236.0,
      "text": "We go on blind dates."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 549260.0,
      "end_time": 552513.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 552537.0,
      "end_time": 553707.0,
      "text": "You know, after all,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 553731.0,
      "end_time": 556236.0,
      "text": "if it doesn&#39;t work out, there&#39;s always tomorrow."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 557381.0,
      "end_time": 559958.0,
      "text": "People over 50 don&#39;t go on blind dates."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 559982.0,
      "end_time": 566982.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 567274.0,
      "end_time": 573810.0,
      "text": "As we age, our time horizons grow shorter and our goals change."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 573602.0,
      "end_time": 576593.0,
      "text": "When we recognize that we don&#39;t have all the time in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 576618.0,
      "end_time": 579465.0,
      "text": "we see our priorities most clearly."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 579489.0,
      "end_time": 582210.0,
      "text": "We take less notice of trivial matters."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 582234.0,
      "end_time": 583735.0,
      "text": "We savor life."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 584400.0,
      "end_time": 586180.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re more appreciative,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 586420.0,
      "end_time": 587797.0,
      "text": "more open to reconciliation."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 588721.0,
      "end_time": 591551.0,
      "text": "We invest in more emotionally important parts of life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 591575.0,
      "end_time": 594236.0,
      "text": "and life gets better,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 594684.0,
      "end_time": 597236.0,
      "text": "so we&#39;re happier day-to-day."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 597565.0,
      "end_time": 599505.0,
      "text": "But that same shift in perspective"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 599529.0,
      "end_time": 603924.0,
      "text": "leads us to have less tolerance than ever for injustice."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 605321.0,
      "end_time": 606896.0,
      "text": "By 2015,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 607397.0,
      "end_time": 610350.0,
      "text": "there will be more people in the United States"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 610590.0,
      "end_time": 613396.0,
      "text": "over the age of 60 than under 15."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 615279.0,
      "end_time": 619441.0,
      "text": "What will happen to societies that are top-heavy with older people?"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 620623.0,
      "end_time": 623915.0,
      "text": "The numbers won&#39;t determine the outcome."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 624470.0,
      "end_time": 625954.0,
      "text": "Culture will."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 627463.0,
      "end_time": 630568.0,
      "text": "If we invest in science and technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 630592.0,
      "end_time": 634582.0,
      "text": "and find solutions for the real problems that older people face"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 635444.0,
      "end_time": 641540.0,
      "text": "and we capitalize on the very real strengths of older people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 642100.0,
      "end_time": 647970.0,
      "text": "then added years of life can dramatically improve quality of life at all ages."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 649157.0,
      "end_time": 653624.0,
      "text": "Societies with millions of talented, emotionally stable citizens"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 653648.0,
      "end_time": 658575.0,
      "text": "who are healthier and better educated than any generations before them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 658599.0,
      "end_time": 662425.0,
      "text": "armed with knowledge about the practical matters of life"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 662449.0,
      "end_time": 666738.0,
      "text": "and motivated to solve the big issues"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 667556.0,
      "end_time": 672323.0,
      "text": "can be better societies than we have ever known."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 674550.0,
      "end_time": 677986.0,
      "text": "My father, who is 92, likes to say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 679380.0,
      "end_time": 682607.0,
      "text": "\"Let&#39;s stop talking only about how to save the old folks"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 682710.0,
      "end_time": 687224.0,
      "text": "and start talking about how to get them to save us all.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 689970.0,
      "end_time": 690537.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 690561.0,
      "end_time": 693355.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}